    "body": "Closes: https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/7559\r\n\r\nAs shared on the issue when having a multi file output on the cache in the form of a zip file the extraction extracts into an incorrect folder structure having the name of the file as part of the path:\r\n```\r\n├── lib_api.h\r\n│   └── lib_api.h\r\n├── lib.cpp\r\n│   └── lib.cpp\r\n├── lib.h\r\n│   └── lib.h\r\n```\r\nor `/tmp/tmp7015iv4v/build/lib_api.h/lib_api.h`\r\n\r\nI've updated a test and validated the test failed without the change (it was a dir instead of a file before).",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-13T18:34:12Z",
